1
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,280
When the brand disappears,

2
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,480
you will leave.

3
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:37,480
Maybe you can think of it this way,

4
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:40,599
before the brand disappears,

5
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:44,000
I will always be by your side.

6
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,319
Has she left?

7
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,080
Do I look good today?

8
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,479
Yes.

9
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,280
Your accessories are also unique.

10
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:36,000
You have it on your face too.

11
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,439
Are you ready for the ball?

12
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:01,360
What does this lyric mean?

13
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,240
Do you understand?

14
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:03,240
Of course.

15
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,280
Then translate it.

16
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:08,199
The general idea is

17
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:09,879
under the full moon,

18
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,960
our roars echo through the night sky,

19
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,319
sharp claws tear through the darkness,

20
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:15,840
just to protect our loved ones.

21
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,520
Actually, I have a secret to tell you.

22
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,000
What secret?

23
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,719
I...

24
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:37,759
I have a friend's

25
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:41,400
friend's friend.

26
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:43,439
He seems

27
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:45,199
different from ordinary humans.

28
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:02,159
Aren't we going to the ball?

29
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,759
I won't force you

30
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:04,680
to do things you don't like.

31
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,639
What kind of dance do you want to do?

32
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:10,680
Rumba,

33
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:11,919
Latin,

34
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,439
or waltz?

35
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:14,960
Which one do you like?

36
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,399
Coincidentally,

37
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:18,519
I don't know any of them.

38
00:04:19,759 --> 00:04:20,920
Then I'll just improvise.

39
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,279
Wait.

40
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:25,959
But

41
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,240
there should be an opening ceremony.

42
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,519
Wolf Clan.

43
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,279
So I left without saying goodbye that day

44
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,480
not because of you,

45
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,920
but because of the full moon.

46
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,360
If I don't hide away,

47
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,399
I'll transform.

48
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:56,839
I'm afraid of hurting you.

49
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:00,360
But you don't need to worry.

50
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:01,800
Tonight is the dark moon night.

51
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,319
I'm no different

52
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:04,879
from ordinary people.

53
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,839
Can't you show me your transformation tonight?

54
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,199
Aren't you afraid?

55
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:20,319
What's there to be afraid of?

56
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,680
It's so cool.

57
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:24,160
And I love furry animals.

58
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,879
You'd better recognize my face now.

59
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,000
When you transform into a wolf next time,

60
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,079
you have to recognize me.

61
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:32,199
and don't bite me.

62
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:33,120
Got it?

63
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:36,560
But

64
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,199
this is my biggest secret.

65
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,519
You can't tell anyone else.

66
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,040
Don't worry.

67
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,199
I know the rules

68
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,480
of the underworld.

69
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,199
You're not believing me at all.

70
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,360
Then

71
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,439
show me.

72
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,959
You can change your ears

73
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,120
or a little tail.

74
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,160
Come on.

75
00:06:01,199 --> 00:06:01,680
See?

76
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,120
I'm not making it up.

77
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,240
Then what do they mean by singing?

78
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,439
♪The moonlight falls on the mountain.♪

79
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:16,160
♪Witnessing the couple's love.♪

80
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,240
♪The ancient ballad sings.♪

81
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,560
♪The lovers♪

82
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,279
♪kiss under the ancient tree.♪

83
00:06:25,319 --> 00:06:26,160
♪The brand is the witness.♪

84
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,519
♪They belong to each other.♪

85
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,240
From the beginning of time,

86
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,040
to the end of time.

87
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,279
Brand.

88
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:38,160
The brand is a special connection

89
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:39,519
for the Wolf Clan.

90
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:42,879
It can leave marks on each other.

91
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,319
Another rumor.

92
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,439
You still can't prove it to me.

93
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:51,399
Boring.

94
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,240
You can't see it.

95
00:07:34,879 --> 00:07:35,279
Right?

96
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:41,279
Maybe I can bite you again

97
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,120
to keep you.

98
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,480
Why didn't you dodge?

99
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,720
Because I know you won't.

100
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:03,480
Is it possible

101
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,399
that I'll do anything to possess you?

102
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,279
Isn't it said

103
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:10,000
that today is your most rational day?

104
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,879
Why are you talking nonsense?

105
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:21,879
Don't leave me.

106
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,360
Lu Zhiyu,

107
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,160
do you know

108
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:33,279
what it feels like to love someone now?

109
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,679
It's now.

110
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:41,480
I love you.

111
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,919
You can choose the freedom you want,

112
00:09:04,159 --> 00:09:05,279
or stay by my side,

113
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:08,480
or go anywhere you want.

114
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:11,120
But the places I want to go

115
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:13,159
are all very far away.

116
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:14,480
That's okay.

117
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:17,039
If you're willing, I can go find you.

118
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,039
Anyway, I run fast,

119
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,320
and I have plenty of time.

120
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,639
But I only have a few decades to live.

121
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:25,600
It's a long time.

122
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:27,879
We agreed

123
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,039
to cherish the present.

124
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,480
This is not the real present.

125
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,279
The police recently cracked a

126
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,000
chain of illegal fishing

127
00:10:40,039 --> 00:10:41,080
and sea transportation.

128
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,440
The head criminal Qin Yeren is on the run.

129
00:10:43,919 --> 00:10:44,840
The police appeal to the public

130
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,000
to provide clues actively.

131
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:46,919
Xie,

132
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,279
you have to help me with this.

133
00:10:48,639 --> 00:10:49,600
You can't just stand by and do nothing.

134
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,600
I can't help.

135
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:53,000
What do you mean you can't help?

136
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:54,639
Then what am I doing this for?

137
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,480
You have to have a conscience.

138
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,000
Between us,

139
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:00,879
there's no need to talk about conscience.

140
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,480
As long as you take on all the charges,

141
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,360
I can guarantee

142
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:09,000
your daughter Qin Yaxin

143
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:11,440
will not be involved or harmed in any way.

144
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:13,320
And I can also guarantee

145
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,840
her life will be comfortable and secure.

146
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,159
Where is Xiaoya?

147
00:11:19,639 --> 00:11:21,039
She's in Lu Zhiyu's turf.

148
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:24,519
If you want her to live well,

149
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,320
just do as I say.
